  (text "USER INTERFACE\n\nFunction:\n- Push buttons (up/down/select)\n- Rotary encoder (temperature adjust)\n- Display connector (OLED/LCD)\n- Status LEDs\n\nKey Components:\n- Tactile switches with debounce\n- Rotary encoder with switch\n- Display connector (I2C)\n- LEDs with current limiting\n\nDebounce:\n- Hardware RC filter\n- 10kΩ pull-up resistors\n- 100nF filter capacitors\n\nDisplay:\n- I2C OLED (SSD1306)\n- Connected via ADUM1250 isolator"
